General.Name: Healthcare AI Acquisition Corp. Warrants
General.Description: Healthcare AI Acquisition Corp. focuses on effecting a merger, share exchange, asset acquisition, share purchase, reorganization, or similar business combination with one or more businesses or entities. It focuses on healthcare and pharmaceutical companies in the e-clinical, healthcare information technology, or outsourced pharmaceutical services industries. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is based in George Town, the Cayman Islands.
